ZH: 我们需要一个温度计来测量室内温度。
EN: We need a thermometer to measure the indoor temperature.

ZH: 医生用温度计来检查病人的体温。
EN: Doctors use thermometers to check patients' body temperature.

ZH: 这个温度计显示的温度非常准确。
EN: The temperature shown on this thermometer is very accurate.

ZH: 我们可以用温度计来监测水温。
EN: We can use a thermometer to monitor the water temperature.

ZH: 温度计显示室外温度已经降到零下了。
EN: The thermometer shows that the outdoor temperature has dropped below zero.

ZH: 我把温度计放在阳光下，让它升温。
EN: I put the thermometer in the sunlight to warm it up.

ZH: 要用温度计测量物体的温度，需要把它插入其中。
EN: To measure the temperature of an object with a thermometer, you need to insert it into the object.

ZH: 温度计可以显示摄氏度或华氏度。
EN: The thermometer can display Celsius or Fahrenheit.

ZH: 请把温度计放在干燥处，避免受潮。
EN: Please keep the thermometer in a dry place to prevent it from getting damp.

ZH: 这款温度计有一个警报功能，能提醒你温度超出正常范围。
EN: This thermometer has an alarm function that can alert you when the temperature exceeds the normal range.

ZH: 用温度计来测量烘烤食物的温度。
EN: Use a thermometer to measure the temperature of baked foods.

ZH: 温度计上的数字在快速上升。
EN: The numbers on the thermometer are rising rapidly.

ZH: 温度计指针指向30度。
EN: The thermometer pointer points to 30 degrees.

ZH: 老师用温度计来教学生如何测量温度。
EN: The teacher uses a thermometer to teach students how to measure temperature.

ZH: 这个温度计需要电池供电。
EN: This thermometer needs to be powered by batteries.

ZH: 小孩子可以用数字简单的温度计来学习数字。
EN: Children can use thermometers with simple numbers to learn about digits.

ZH: 每个家庭都应该备有一个温度计。
EN: Every household should have a thermometer.

ZH: 温度计可以帮助我们预防热病。
EN: Thermometers can help us prevent heat illnesses.

ZH: 温度计的读数会随着气温的变化而变化。
EN: The thermometer reading will change with the temperature.

ZH: 这个温度计有一个很大的显示屏，非常方便观察。
EN: This thermometer has a large display screen, which is very convenient for observation.
